        "$$ \\psi_n(x)=\\sqrt{\\frac{2}{L}}\\sin{\\left(\\frac{n\\pi}{L}x\\right)} $$\n",
        "Primer necessitem importal les següents llibreries (per a aquesta part en concret):"

        "\n",
        "Primer caldrà determinal la llargada de la caixa unidimensional (***L***)."

        "x_list = np.linspace(0,L,100)       # Aquest són els valors que necessitem per a poder fer les gràfiques"

      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "egy3aNseHcQQ"

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "def psi(n,L,x):\n",
        "    return np.sqrt(2/L)*np.sin(n*np.pi*x/L)\n",
        "def psi_2(n,L,x):\n",
        "    return np.square(psi(n,L,x))"

        "## ***Caixa bidimensional***\n",
        "També es pot fer el mateix per una caixa bidimensional.\n",
        "\n",
        "Evidentment, l'equació a utilitzar canviarà:\n",
        "$$ \\psi_n(x,y)=\\sqrt{\\frac{2}{L_x}}\\sqrt{\\frac{2}{L_y}}\\sin{\\left(\\frac{n\\pi}{L_x}x\\right)\\sin{\\left(\\frac{n\\pi}{L_y}y\\right)}} $$\n",
        "Igual que amb l'exemple anterior, primer definirem algunes de les variables com $n$, $L_x$ i $L_y$."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "UIzD8aqDLDJi"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "n = 1\n",
        "\n",
        "Lx = 1**-10\n",
        "Ly = 1**-10\n",
        "\n",
        "x,y = np.linspace(0, Lx, 200), np.linspace(0, Ly, 200)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Ax = np.sqrt(2/Lx)\n",
        "# Ay = np.sqrt(2/Ly)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "I8c_WAt0WYKd"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "Ara definim la funció"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "6fuKsmgMWtRz"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "def psi_3d(a,b):\n",
        "  return np.sqrt(2/Lx)*np.sqrt(2/Ly)*np.sin(n*np.pi*a/Lx)*np.sin(n*np.pi*b/Ly)\n",
        "def psi2_3d(a,b):\n",
        "  # return (np.sin((n*np.pi *a)/Lx)*np.sin((n*np.pi*b)/Lx))**2\n",
        "  return np.square(psi_3d(a,b))"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "NlQW562yWvWT"

        "PSI = psi.reshape(X.shape)\n",

        "fig = pyplt.figure(figsize=(8,6))\n",

        "# **Gràfica de la part radial d'orbitals**"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "r3sBGeJe6xOk"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "tG7n8bc06mm-"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "%matplotlib inline\n",
        "import math"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "Generarem l'orbital 3s de l'hidrogen segona la formula\n",
        "\n",
        "$$ \\psi_{3s} = \\frac{2}{27}\\sqrt{3}(2r^{2/9} - 2r + 3)e^{-r/3} $$\n",
        "\n",
        "Primer definim la funció amb el paquet *math* per a poder posar l'arrel i els exponents i després generem les dades que ens permetran graficar la part radial de l'orbital 3s."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "HmFd4ind7Yay"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# definició de la funció\n",
        "def orbital_3S(r):\n",
        "    wf = (2/27)*math.sqrt(3)*(2*r**2/9 - 2*r + 3)* math.exp(-r/3)\n",
        "    return wf\n",
        "\n",
        "# generació de les dades\n",
        "r = [num / 3 for num in range(1, 150, 3)]            # aquí estem generat valors entre 1 i 150 cada 3 números: 1,4,7...147,150\n",
        "psi_3s = [orbital_3S(num)/4 for num in r]"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "HRO2YaOF6-KP"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "Ara ja tenim els punts que es volen graficar, ara només cal implementar-los a la gràfica."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "xzK-1lpM8NqS"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "plt.title(\"Part radial de l'orbital 3s\")\n",
        "plt.plot(r, psi_3s, '-', label='Orbital 3s')\n",
        "plt.hlines(0, 0, 50, linestyle='dashed', color='C1')\n",
        "plt.legend()\n",
        "plt.show()"
